comments: Dr. Mena was the best professor in the EDCO program at SJSU. She challenged her students and always gave great feedback. There was a lot of work in the course, but I learned a lot from her class. She made herself available to meet with students and responded to emails in a timely manner.

comments: i would recommend students take Dr. Mena to all students who are "nervous, scared, intimidated, concerned" about writing their thesis. She breaks down the process in easy to follow, easy to do steps. She also offers excellent feedback that will help you make your thesis paper better. And she will EDIT IT FOR FREE!!!!
